','','Community & Support','','publish','closed','closed','','support','','','2016-06-08 09:10:35','2016-06-08 09:10:35','',0,'http://192.168.1.76/Projects/ykings/?page_id=628',0,'page','',0),(631,1,'2015-10-27 08:57:09','2015-10-27 08:57:09','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Progress is the name of the game</strong></p>\nWithin the Ykings coaching function you will come across the progression formula. The progression formula is your healthy and most efficient way to progress to your goals.\n\nWe have demystified the most epic moves and elite skills from competitive gymnastics, calisthenics and bodyweigth training into simple &amp; doable progressions that lead to a final exercise. Learn with the progression formula, get challenged by the coach and master all skills to reach the hall of fame.\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Conquer a whole new world in five steps</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Unlock skills and exercises as you get stronger. Once you master them get ready to be pushed from your coach to evolve and progress further. The progression formula will help you achieve your personal goals and perfectly adjusts the workouts with your coach to your preferences and skills. Go along the path of constant challenges.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Get stronger, become flexible, be a mover!</p>','Progression Formula','','publish','closed','closed','','progression-formula','','','2015-10-27 08:57:09','2015-10-27 08:57:09','',0,'http://192.168.1.76/Projects/ykings/?page_id=631',0,'page','',0),(634,1,'2015-10-27 08:57:17','2015-10-27 08:57:17','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Back to the roots of fitness</strong></p>\nHIIT is a training idea in which low to moderate intensity intervals are alternated with high intensity intervals.\n\nThe original idea of High Intensity Interval Training (HIIT) was to create a more challenging running routine. HIIT is considered to be much more effective than normal cardio because the intensity is higher and you are able to increase both your aerobic and anaerobic endurance while burning more fat than ever before.\n\n<a href=\"http://ykings.com/New/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/art-alley-run.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1032\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-1032\" src=\"http://ykings.com/New/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/art-alley-run-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"art-alley-run\" width=\"455\" height=\"341\" /></a>\n\nYkings is reviving the original idea of HIIT and the coach will challenge you with short but intense running sessions from time to time that will boost your metabolism.\n\nResearch on HIIT has shown that the intense bursts burn adipose tissue more effectively than low-intensity exercise - up to 50% more efficiently. It has also been shown to speed up your metabolism which helps you burn more calories throughout the day.\n\nTry it out and you will see, until then please subscribe to our mailing list.','HIIT','','publish','closed','closed','','hiit','','','2015-10-27 08:57:17','2015-10-27 08:57:17','',0,'http://192.168.1.76/Projects/ykings/?page_id=634',0,'page','',0),(637,1,'2015-10-27 08:57:38','2015-10-27 08:57:38','If you need our assistance with any problem please contact us via email <strong>support@ykings.com</strong> or our contact form which you will find <a href=\"http://ykings.com/New/index.php/contact/\"><strong>here.</strong> </a>\r\n\r\nBrowse through our <strong><a href=\"http://ykings.com/New/index.php/faq/\">FAQs</a></strong> and see if you questions might have been answered already.\r\n\r\nFeel free to send us all other questions &amp; feedback. We will do our best to get back to you directly.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Help &amp; Support','','publish','closed','closed','','help-support','','','2016-06-07 18:00:15','2016-06-07 18:00:15','',0,'http://192.168.1.76/Projects/ykings/?page_id=637',0,'page','',0),(640,1,'2015-10-27 08:58:18','2015-10-27 08:58:18','<span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>Ykings PBT</strong></span> was developed to br