 fitness levels.</li>\r\n 	<li>Beginners as well as advanced athletes will find a goal to pursue with the sport. Besides the standard claims of many sports and fitness programms, bodyweight training does not only increase your general fitness and get you in great shape, but provides multiple benefits in addition for you.</li>\r\n 	<li>Proper bodyweight training will promote the growth of lean muscle mass, and increase your strength, mobility, flexibility, agility, and endurance.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nAs you see from the list of benefits of the sport, there is a fine line to <strong><a href=\"http://ykings.com/index.php/competitive-gymnastics/\">competitive gymnastics</a></strong>. In Ykings PBT we embedded the adaptive nature of the sport in a comprehensive workout concept. If you want to be more than just fit, let us hunt down skills and evolve you to a bodyweight master. Welcome to our world.\r\n\r\n</div>','Bodyweight Training & Calisthenics','','publish','closed','closed','','what-is-calisthenics','','','2016-08-30 10:36:25','2016-08-30 10:36:25','',0,'http://ykings.com/New/?page_id=1415',0,'page','',0),(1416,1,'2016-06-06 17:11:04','2016-06-06 17:11:04','','Calisthenics','','inherit','closed','closed','','1415-revision-v1','','','2016-06-06 17:11:04','2016-06-06 17:11:04','',1415,'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/06/1415-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1417,1,'2016-06-06 17:13:50','2016-06-06 17:13:50','The sport behind the workout concept','Calisthenics','','inherit','closed','closed','','1415-revision-v1','','','2016-06-06 17:13:50','2016-06-06 17:13:50','',1415,'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/06/1415-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1418,1,'2016-06-06 17:16:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Free vs Pro','What to expect?','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2016-06-06 17:16:15','2016-06-06 17:16:15','',0,'http://ykings.com/New/?page_id=1418',0,'page','',0),(1419,1,'2016-06-06 17:15:00','2016-06-06 17:15:00','Free vs Pro','What to expect?','','inh