f0b300;\"><strong>Learn progressive bodyweight training with the community</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1nPuqNWK8uU\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\">\r\n</iframe></p>\r\nYKMS stands for Ykings Mannfall Sessions. YKMS are free public workout sessions which are offered to create interest of the gereal public in the sport. We are supporting local groups to offer YKMS as a introduction to the sport with a set standard.\r\n\r\nThe mission is to help all athletes of different fitness and skill levels to progress to the next level or simply get a feeling of what the sport is all about.\r\n\r\nYKMS provides a unique and valuable social education and experience to the world of progressive bodyweight training. It provides an ideal opportunity to learn about teamwork, motivation, fun, sportsmanship and dedication.\r\n\r\nMastering bodyweight skills requires a great amount of patience, dedication, perseverance and planning. Prior to a YKMS, participants have the opportunity (via facebook) to vote for the bodyweight skills they want to learn.YKMS follow a simple schedule that is altered a bit by the local groups which looks like this.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Warmup</li>\r\n 	<li>Mobility ession</li>\r\n 	<li>Skill and progression training (according to community vote)</li>\r\n 	<li>HIIT &amp; full body workout</li>\r\n 	<li>Cooldown &amp; stretching</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEverybody is welcome, we always have a beginner class that provides an introduction to the sport. Feel free to join us. Check our <strong><a href=\"http://ykings.com/New/index.php/our-events/\">events webpage</a></strong> or sign in over facebook.\r\n\r\n[facebook id=\"facebook_53\" links=\"https://www.facebook.com/official.ykings/\" width=\"\" layout=\"standard\" colorscheme=\"light\" sendbutton=\"false\" showfaces=\"false\" ]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in getting YKMS to your city,<strong> <a href=\"http://ykings.com/New/index.php/contact/\">contact us</a></strong>. Become a partner and do your part to bring the sport forward.','YKMS','','publish','closed','closed','','ykms','','','2016-08-31 13:27:22','2016-08-31 13:27:22','',0,'http://ykings.com/New/?page_id=1424',0,'page','',0),(1425,1,'2016-06-06 17:36:02','2016-06-06 17:36:02','','YKMS','','inherit','closed','closed','','1424-revision-v1','','','2016-06-06 17:36:02','2016-06-06 17:36:02','',1424,'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/06/1424-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1427,1,'2016-06-06 18:09:01','2016-06-06 18:09:01','Ykings GmbH was founded in November 2015 by sports enthusiasts and professionals. The young company is focused on providing state of the art fitness &amp; health solutions via smartphone applications.\r\n\r\nThe first version of the app was released in May 2016. The company is well connected with the popular disciplines calisthenics, gymnastics and bodyweight training. To support beginners but also to provide a high level of versatility to advanced athletes, demanding skills were broken down into essential step by step exercises (progressions) and support exercises (allies).\r\n\r\nThe solution provided is a fully adaptive workout and training experience that considers fitness and skill level, weekly availability and intensity. The workout concept is made for beginners and advanced athletes and is independent of time and place. It can be used alone or with a community of like-minded athletes. Download from the app stores - for iOS and Android.','About us','','inherit','closed','closed','','646-revision-v1','','','2016-06-06 18:09:01','2016-06-06 18:09:01','',646,'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/06/646-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1428,1,'2016-06-07 18:06:43','2016-06-07 18:06:43','We are constantly looking for driven online marketers and tech-savvy developers of all kinds.\r\n\r\nGet in touch with us if you believe you are the perfect fit.\r\n\r\n#WeGrowT