 10:19:03','',0,'http://ykings.com/New/?p=1515',29,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1516,1,'2016-06-08 14:03:39','2016-06-08 14:03:39',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1516','','','2016-07-04 10:19:03','2016-07-04 10:19:03','',0,'http://ykings.com/New/?p=1516',30,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1517,1,'2016-08-30 10:42:02','2016-08-30 10:42:02','<span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>Progressive Bodyweight Traininig</strong></span> is made of the disciplines <strong><a href=\"http://ykings.com/what-is-calisthenics/\">bodyweight training</a></strong> and <a href=\"http://ykings.com/index.php/competitive-gymnastics/\"><strong>gymnastics</strong></a>. Both sports are reknown for the most demanding body control and challenging bodyweight skills.<strong>\n</strong>\n\nMastering a bodyweight skill requires a systematic step by step approach. The adaptive nature of the sport and the progress towards a skill is embedded in essential exercises called progressions. This is why at Ykings we refer our workout concept to progressive bodyweight training (PBT).\n\nProgressive bodyweight training (PBT) secures gradual development towards advanced bodyweight exercises and skills such as the muscleup, human flag, front lever to name a few.\n\nThe purpose of the Ykings workout concept is to guide you efficiently and healthy towards mastering your most desirable bodyweight skills. Consider to workout not only for your fitness, but strength, body control and skills and many more beneficial body characteristics at the same time.\n\n<em>#StriveForProgress</em>','Progressive Bodyweight Training (PBT)','','inherit','closed','closed','','616-autosave-v1','','','2016-08-30 10:42:02','2016-08-30 10:42:02','',616,'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/08/616-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1518,1,'2016-06-08 14:15:21','2016-06-08 14:15:21','Ykings is mainly based on the disciplines calisthenics and gymnastics. Both sports are reknown for the most demanding and challenging skills and moves in bodyweight training.<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nMastering a skill requires to go at it step by step. The adaptive nature of the sport and your progress towards a skill is embedded in essential exercises called progressions. This is why at Ykings we talk about progressive bodyweight training.\r\n\r\nProgressive bodyweight training (PBT) secures gradual development towards advanced bodyweight exercises and elite skills such as the muscleup, human flag, front lever and many more.\r\n\r\nThe purpose of the Ykings workout concept is to guide you efficiently and healthy towards mastering your most desirable bodyweight skills. Consider to workout not only for your fitness, but strength, body control and skills at the same time.\r\n\r\n<em>#StriveForProgress</em>','The sport behind Ykings','','inherit','closed','closed','','616-revision-v1','','','2016-06-08 14:15:21','2016-06-08 14:15:21','',616,'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/08/616-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1519,1,'2016-06-08 14:51:45','2016-06-08 14:51:45','<div id=\"cc-m-8363560395\" class=\"j-module n j-text \">\r\n\r\nThe word <strong><i>calisthenics</i></strong> comes from the ancient Greek words <i>kálos</i> (κάλλος), which means \"beauty\", and <i>sthénos</i> (σθένος), meaning \"strength\". Calisthenics is raw and pure bodyweight training and also known as Street Workout. One of the greatest advantages of bodyweight training is that you can do it anywhere, anytime, and there are easier and more advanced exercises to start or evolve with.\r\n\r\nBeginners as well as advanced athletes will find a goal to pursue with the sport. Besides the standard claims of many sports and fitness programms, calisthenics does not only increase your general fitness and get you in great shape, but provides multiple benefits in addition for you.\r\n\r\nProper calisthenics training will promote the growth of lean muscle mass, and increase your strength, mobility, flexibility, agility, and endurance.\r\n\r\nAs you see from the list of benefits of the sport, there is a fine line to competitive gymnastics. In the Ykings workout concept we embedded the adaptive nature of the sport in a comprehensive progressive bodyweight training concept. If you want to be more than just fit, let us hunt down skills and evolve you to a bodyweight master. Welcome to our world.\r\n\r\n</div>','What is Calisthenics?','','inherit','closed','closed','','1415-revision-v1','','','2016-06-08 14:51:45','2016-06-08 14:51:45','',1415,'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/08/1415-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1521,1,'2016-08-30 10:13:11','2016-08-30 10:13:11','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Get ready to be pushed\n</strong></p>\nYkings is divided in a free basic version and YkingsPro. YkingsPro includes a dynamic coach, who creates workout weeks and skill trainings on a subscription basis according to your prefernces.\n<div id=\"ufaq-body-3r7-1451-11\" class=\"ufaq-faq-body ufaq-body-1451\">\n<div id=\"ufaq-post-1451\" class=\"ewd-ufaq-post-margin ufaq-faq-post\">\n\nWe have developed YkingsPro for those of you, who seek an adaptive path to work on their body transformation and simply want to pursue skills while getting stronger and fitter. YkingsPro includes the following benefits compared to the free version:\n<ul>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>No limits</strong></span> - access all workouts, excercises, skills, progressions and HIIT runs</li>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>Personalized workout plans</strong></span> - take advantage of weekly workout plans which are dynamically adapted to your feedback\n<ul>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">availability</li>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">workout intensity</li>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">focus track</li>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">raids</li>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">skill- and fitness level</li>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">goals</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>Full workout days</strong></span> - progress in a healthy way. Get various warmups, fundamentals (pre-workout, dynamic stretching and mobility), workouts (circuit-, sets &amp; reps training) and stretching routines</li>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>Skill raids</strong></span> – pick your wanted skill and receive professional skill trainings to push your progress to the next level</li>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>Progression formula</strong></span> – master elite skills (muscleup, front lever, human flag and more) with essential step by step progressions and ally exercises automatically integrated in your workouts</li>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>Guidance</strong></span> – all progressions and exercises include video tutorials with pro tips and range of motion</li>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>Freestyle</strong></span> – track your own workout sessions and log them in your profile</li>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>Community</strong></span> – share &amp; receive tips and tricks from other athletes, friends and featured athletes &amp; find athletes and trainings spots around to you</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>','YkingsPro - This Is What You Can Expect','','inherit','closed','closed','','620-autosave-v1','','','2016-08-30 10:13:11','2016-08-30 10:13:11','',620,'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/09/620-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1522,1,'2016-06-09 07:03:22','2016-06-09 07:03:22','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Get ready to be pushed\r\n</strong></p>\r\nYkings includes a dynamic coaching function (Coach) that compiles weekly workout plans to your personal preferences. Your virtual coach will develop your body awareness and get you closer to your set goals, 100% tailor-made and adjusted to your fitness level. With the coach you get workout plans that not only get you fit, but strong &amp; skilled at the same time.\r\n\r\nThe coach considers your skill level at all times and will challenge you weekly to progress efficiently. Become comfortable, being uncomfortable and conquer set goals in small guided doable steps. Doesn\'t matter if you just started or if you are an old hand at sports. A library of videos will guide you through your workouts if needed.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ykings.com/New/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/iStock_000051423662_Large-e1455113998137.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1112\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1112\" src=\"http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/iStock_000051423662_Large-684x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"423\" height=\"634\" /></a>\r\n\r\nBesides your personal goals, the Coach will consider your preferences such as\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>availability,</li>\r\n 	<li>intensity,</li>\r\n 	<li>muscle group</li>\r\n 	<li>fitness &amp; skill level.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Learn / Evolve /Master</strong></p>\r\nAs you evolve through the multi-level learning program <a href=\"http://ykings.com/?page_id=631\"><strong>– the progression formula -</strong></a>  you will be able to track and master your strength and skill level. The Progression Formula breaks demanding exercises down into progressions which the coach integrates in your workouts. We demystify demanding exercises such as the one arm pushup, muscleups and many others so that they will become achievable for you.\r\n\r\nSpecify the skills you want to work for and the coach will make sure you learn them. Join Ykings - the healthy step by step approach to achieve your goals - fully customizeable with state of the art smartphone applications.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">#WeGrowTogether #StriveForProgress</p>','Ykings Coach','','inherit','closed','closed','','620-revision-v1','','','2016-06-09 07:03:22','2016-06-09 07:03:22','',620,'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/09/620-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1523,1,'2016-06-09 07:08:07','2016-06-09 07:08:07','[vc_row][vc_colu