dth=\"647\" height=\"431\" /></a> Explosive pushups. Bam![/caption]\r\n\r\nI am an addict to the sport and still progressing. I also want to push the body centered movement further as a whole. Personally I am working to get the planche. Follow me to see closely what I am up to towards achieving that goal.\r\n\r\nFind me in the app under - <strong>Flex_st</strong>','Flex_st: On the way to new goals','','inherit','closed','closed','','1593-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-13 08:39:46','2016-06-13 08:39:46','',1593,'http://ykings.com/index.php/2016/06/13/1593-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1625,1,'2016-06-13 08:56:35','2016-06-13 08:56:35',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1625','','','2016-07-04 10:19:01','2016-07-04 10:19:01','',0,'http://ykings.com/?p=1625',19,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1626,1,'2016-06-13 09:00:30','2016-06-13 09:00:30','We are working with well chosen cooperation partners.\n\nJoin our team with your crew, equipment, apps and any other product that will help others to succeed.\n\nIf you are interested in a win-win partnership with us don\'t hesistate to contact us via email <strong>business(a)ykings.com</strong> or our <a href=\"http://ykings.com/New/index.php/contact/\">contact form</a>.\n\n&nbsp;','Partner','','inherit','closed','closed','','1481-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-13 09:00:30','2016-06-13 09:00:30','',1481,'http://ykings.com/index.php/2016/06/13/1481-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1627,1,'2016-06-13 09:01:55','2016-06-13 09:01:55','We are working with well chosen cooperation partners and constantly looking for strong partners to push the sport.\r\n\r\nJoin us on our mission with your crew, equipment, apps and any other product that will help others to succeed.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in a win-win partnership don\'t hesistate to contact us via email <strong>business(a)ykings.com</strong> or our <a href=\"http://ykings.com/New/index.php/contact/\">contact form</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Partner','','inherit','closed','closed','','1481-