Munich finally has a calisthenics park. Everybody around is invited to join us to our public workout sessions. We start','YKMS Munich','','inherit','closed','closed','','1375-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-22 15:30:46','2016-06-22 15:30:46','',1375,'http://ykings.com/index.php/2016/06/22/1375-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1656,1,'2016-06-23 07:14:51','2016-06-23 07:14:51','','IMG_2405','','inherit','open','closed','','img_2405','','','2016-06-23 07:14:51','2016-06-23 07:14:51','',1375,'http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/IMG_2405.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1657,1,'2016-06-24 07:31:06','2016-06-24 07:31:06','','Koalabars','','publish','closed','closed','','koalabars','','','2016-06-24 07:31:06','2016-06-24 07:31:06','',0,'http://ykings.com/index.php/organizer/koalabars/',0,'tribe_organizer','',0),(1658,1,'2016-06-27 16:41:52','2016-06-27 16:41:52','Hi,\r\nmy name is Roman and I am a student from Frankfurt. All my life I have been in love with movement, sports and an active lifestyle. I have done a lot of sports from different styles of fighting to windsurfing and skiing.\r\nThe most important thing for me has always been: how can I get stronger, faster, more flexible and more active. All in all – how can I get better than I was yesterday.\r\nI was always looking out for a new way to build strength, flexibility and stumbled upon Calisthenics. Calisthenics – the sport of natural movement and maximum strength. The sport that makes you stand out from the crowd. Calisthenics is for every single person out there! I tried it out and very soon it became a big part of my life.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_995\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"268\"]<a href=\"http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/ShrpkRVSTMGY7DmBnvyRg_D4pIekmP7R_DUc-pB5AW4.jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1659 aligncenter\" src=\"http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/ShrpkRVSTMGY7DmBnvyRg_D4pIekmP7R_DUc-pB5AW4-683x1024.jpeg\" alt=\"ShrpkRVSTMGY7DmBnvyRg_D4pIekmP7R_DUc-pB5AW4\" width=\"268\" height=\"401\" /></a> Handstand[/caption]\r\n\r\nAfter the first workouts with Calisthenics Frankfurt I became stonger and more energetic. I strived for more pullups, different push-ups and wanted to learn new moves and skills.\r\nAfter about one year of Calisthenics I took part in a bar-battle in Austria. In July 2015 I was also at the German championship in Bremen and world cup stage in Stuttgart. I got to know a lot of people which today I can call my dear friends and which also are an important part of my life.\r\n\r\nEveryday I train. Everyday I improve, even if it’s only one step at a time. And everyday I see people holding themselves back because of some lame excuse. „This is too hard for me“, „If I only had enough time…“, „I am too old for this“ and so on. Being also a coach, let me tell you \"I’ve heard it all!\"\r\n\r\nIs it really too hard for you? – If you haven’t tried yet, this excuse won’t count. :-)\r\nYou don’t have enough time? – well guess what, I study, I work, I have friends, family and all the obligatory everyday activities too! But I take the time for my health, and so should you!\r\n\r\nTake time for the things that matter. Remember, you only have one body and one health. We, modern humans, don’t live the healthiest lifestyles. We work a lot, sleep little, drink alcohol, smoke cigarettes and don’t eat properly. If you ask me, the least you can do for your body is get your a** up, train hard and ultimately feel better. A well spent hour of your life everyday can make a change and it most definitely doesn’t hurt. If anything, it’s fun, good for your brain and good for your health!\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_995\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"900\"]<a href=\"http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/VorrjuUO17PX6MvvbrOzPf-0gTypZy41Wpb1I3sS5y8.jpeg\"><img class=\"size-large wp-image-1661 aligncenter\" src=\"http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/VorrjuUO17PX6MvvbrOzPf-0gTypZy41Wpb1I3sS5y8-1024x683.jpeg\" alt=\"VorrjuUO17PX6MvvbrOzPf-0gTypZy41Wpb1I3sS5y8\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a> Backlever[/caption]\r\n\r\nI could go on and on and tell you why all the excuses won’t give you anything. But instead I would like to introduce you step by step, little by little into the world of Calisthenics. My sport, my love, my life! It’s easy and I will guide you. If you have any questions - go ahead and ask.\r\nI have been giving the weekly group workouts of Calisthenics Frankfurt for sometimes 100 people at a time. At the moment I give Calisthenics classes in one of the big gyms in Frankfurt and I’d love to help!\r\nMy own motivation to do all this is very simple: from all the things you have and will have in life, in the end only on thing really matters. That thing is your well being and your health. I think it’s worth to invest a few hours a week and with that – invest in yourself!\r\nCome with me and I will show you a wonderful world full of good people, a healthy lifestyle and a very bright future for your body and your mind. Because the moment your body gets fit, your mind will follow.\r\n\r\nFind me in the app - <strong>Roman Keyfman</strong> -','Roman Keyfman: The moment your body gets fit, your mind will follow','','draft','closed','closed','','roman-keyfman-the-moment-your-body-gets-fit-your-mind-will-follow','','','2016-09-05 07:03:43','2016-09-05 07:03:43','',0,'http://ykings.com/?post_type=post-portfolio&#038;p=1658',0,'post-portfolio','',0),(1659,1,'2016-06-27 15:23:44','2016-06-27 15:23:44','','ShrpkRVSTMGY7DmBnvyRg_D4pIekmP7R_DUc-pB5AW4','','inherit','open','closed','','shrpkrvstmgy7dmbnvyrg_d4piekmp7r_duc-pb5aw4','','','2016-06-27 15:23:44','2016-06-27 15:23:44','',1658,'http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/ShrpkRVSTMGY7DmBnvyRg_D4pIekmP7R_DUc-pB5AW4.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1660,1,'2016-06-27 15:23:52','2016-06-27 15:23:52','','uLHutVP88NVq0dIU4Ntd_u34MdYP7hAbZCFCK-zurtk','','inherit','open','closed','','ulhutvp88nvq0diu4ntd_u34mdyp7habzcfck-zurtk',