,0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1707,1,'2016-07-14 10:10:26','2016-07-14 10:10:26','Together with Calisthenics Olfen, we are proud to present our first public workout session in the upcoming week. Meet the community, learn the sport and most importantly have fun together. Any skill and fitness level welcome.','YKMS Olfen','','publish','open','closed','','ykms-olfen','','','2016-07-14 10:10:26','2016-07-14 10:10:26','',0,'http://ykings.com/?post_type=tribe_events&#038;p=1707',0,'tribe_events','',0),(1708,1,'2016-07-14 10:10:26','2016-07-14 10:10:26','','Calisthenics Olfen','','publish','closed','closed','','calisthenics-olfen','','','2016-07-14 10:10:26','2016-07-14 10:10:26','',0,'http://ykings.com/index.php/organizer/calisthenics-olfen/',0,'tribe_organizer','',0),(1709,1,'2016-07-14 10:10:26','2016-07-14 10:10:26','','Wieschhof Halle','','publish','closed','closed','','wieschhof-halle','','','2016-07-14 10:10:26','2016-07-14 10:10:26','',0,'http://ykings.com/index.php/venue/wieschhof-halle/',0,'tribe_venue','',0),(1710,1,'2016-07-15 14:48:54','2016-07-15 14:48:54','After reading this article you will know\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>what business people can learn from pro athletes and vice versa</li>\r\n 	<li>the underlying pattern of quotes from pro athletes</li>\r\n 	<li>how your thoughts dictate what you are doing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe sports and the business world are a lot alike. There\'s training and preparation, goals, competition, wins and losses, passion and emotions, and a lot of hard work. The similarities are astonishing. However, when it comes down to pro athletes and really thriving businesses we found a pretty clear pattern that sorts the wheat from the chaff.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Here are our findings of highly successful people in sports and business:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>They plan, do and repeat with a high sense of urgency and dedication</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>They are able to stay focused on the things that really matter in the face of a multitude of potential distractions</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>They are able to bounce back from setbacks with a determination and intense desire to succeed</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>They are able to maintain their belief in themselves in the most trying circumstances</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSo this is our short and crucial list understanding the mindset of pro athletes and successful business leaders. The trigger to write this article was <strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RZNFH-jH-eo\">Reebok’s new commercial headlining Ronda Rousey</a>.</strong> The former Women bantamweight champion of the UFC, just announced her comeback in amazing fashion after an upset loss that ended a 12-fight unbeaten run in the UFC. Let’s look at a selection of the best sport quotes that should help you to recognize the pattern as well and inspire you for your future goals.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>\"Here\'s the thing about being perfect. Perfect never gets truly tested. Perfect never gets to silence its critics. Perfect never gets a shot at redemption. So yeah. I\'m fine not being perfect.\"</strong> <em>Ronda Rousey, former UFC Women bantamweight champion</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>“There are only two options regarding commitment. You’re either IN or you’re OUT. There is no such thing as life in-between.” </strong><em>Pat Riley, former NBA coach\r\n</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>“I hated every minute of training, but I said, ‘Don’t quit. Suffer now and live the rest of your life as a champion.\"</strong> <em>Muhammad Ali\r\n</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>If you aren\'t going all the way, why go at all?\" </strong><em>Joe Namath, Hall of Fame football quarterback (1965-1977)</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>\"In baseball and in business, there are three types of people. Those who make it happen, those who watch it happen, and those who wonder what happened.\"</strong><em>Tommy Lasorda, Hall of Fame baseball player and manager (1954-1956, player; 1976-1996, manager)</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>“I laugh and joke, but I don\'t get distracted very easily.”</strong> <em>Lebron James, NBA player of the Cleveland Cavaliers</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>“There’s no talent here, this is hard work. This is an obsession. Talent does not exist. We are all equals as human beings. You could be anyone if you put in the time. You will reach the top, and that’s that. I am not talented, I am obsessed.” </strong><em>Conor McGregor, current UFC featherweight champion</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhether you are pushing your next career step or setting your next personal fitness goals, we hope you see that everything starts with you. The conclusion is that a positive and resilient mindset underpins your drive and ability to continuously excel in your craft. How bad do you want it, is the question that remains.\r\n\r\n<strong>Ykings is the home of the ambitious athlete. If you are bored with workout programs whose primary goals is to get you fit only, challenge yourself with progressive bodyweight training and push for the next level. Get strong and skilled while getting fit. Hunt down multiple goals. Are you ready to go the whole way? Let us know.</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','What can be learned from motivational sport quotes?','','publish','open','open','','what-can-be-learned-from-motivational-sport-quotes','','','2016-07-15 17:15:55','2016-07-15 17:15:55','',0,'http://ykings.com/?p=1710',0,'post','',0),(1711,1,'2016-07-15 14:45:45','2016-07-15 14:45:45','','mot','','inherit','open','closed','','mot','','','2016-07-15 14:45:45','2016-07-15 14:45:45','',1710,'http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/mot.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1712,1,'2016-07-15 14:48:54','2016-07-15 14:48:54','After reading this article you will know\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>what business people can learn from pro athletes and vice versa</li>\r\n 	<li>the under