ering your most desirable bodyweight skills. Consider to workout not only for your fitness, but strength, body control and skills and many more beneficial body characteristics at the same time.\r\n\r\n<em>#StriveForProgress</em>','Progressive Bodyweight Training (PBT)','','inherit','closed','closed','','616-revision-v1','','','2016-08-29 15:46:52','2016-08-29 15:46:52','',616,'http://ykings.com/616-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1729,1,'2016-08-30 10:45:23','2016-08-30 10:45:23','<span style=\"color: #f0b300;\"><strong>Gymnastics</strong></span> as an Olympic event have been so far the most well-developed form of bodyweight skills. This wide recognition and popularity makes Gymnastics the most influential form of bodyweight training.\n\nAlthough gymnastics is by itself a broad term and contains a variety of different disciplines… the main goal is to develop a large variety of athletic qualities, such us strength, agility, coordination, flexibility, self-control, kinesthetic awareness, etc. For this reason Gymnastics builds the core of Ykings PBT and is probably the mother of bodyweight training.\n\nMost gymnasts and bodyweight athletes are in an amazing physical shape. Our athletes are among the strongest and most flexible on a pound for pound comparsion. This is the main reason why the sport is attractive for everybody out there who ultimately does not want to look like a bodybuilder. Build natural lean muscles while you work on other athletic qualities.\n\nGymnastics includes a wide variety of exercises and insane skills. At Ykings we combined both worlds and embedded the versatility of gymnastics in a progressive bodyweight training platform.','Gymnastics','','inherit','closed','closed','','1679-autosave-v1','','','2016-08-30 10:45:23','2016-08-30 10:45:23','',1679,'http://ykings.com/1679-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1730,1,'2016-08-29 16:04:14','2016-08-29 16:04:14','Gymnastics as an Olympic event have been so far the most well-developed form of bodyweight skills. This wide recognition and popularity makes gymnastics the most influential form of bodyweight training.\r\n\r\nAlthough gymnastics is by itself a broad term and contains a variety of different disciplines… the main goal is to develop a large variety of athletic qualities, such us strength, agility, coordination, flexibility, self-control, kinesthetic awareness, etc. For this reason Gymnastics builds the core of Ykings PBT and is probably the mother of bodyweight training.\r\n\r\nMost gymnasts and bodyweight athletes are in an amazing physical shape. Our athletes are among the strongest and most flexible on a pound for pound comparsion. This is the main reason why the sport is attractive for everybody out there who ultimately does not want to look like a bodybuilder. Build natural lean muscles while you work on other athletic qualities.\r\n\r\nGymnastics includes a wide variety of exercises and insane skills. At Ykings we combined both worlds and embedded the versatility of gymnastics in a progressive bodyweight training platform.','Competitive Gymnastics','','inherit','closed','closed','','1679-revision-v1','','','2016-08-29 16:04:14','2016-08-29 16:04:14','',1679,'http://ykings.com/1679-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1731,1,'2016-08-29 17:03:45','2016-08-29 17:03:45','<div id=\"cc-m-8363560395\" class=\"j-module n j-text \">\r\n\r\n<strong>Bodyweight training</strong> refers to exercises that are done in a rhythmic, systematic way using your body weight for resistance. An advanced form of bodyweight training is calisthenics, which is also known as street workout.\r\n\r\n<em>The word calisthenics comes from the ancient Greek words kálos (κάλλος), which means \"beauty\", and sthénos (σθένος), meaning \"strength\". Calisthenics is raw and pure bodyweight training and also known as Street Workout.</em>\r\n\r\nThe benefits of bodyweight training are translated into Ykings PBT\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>One of the greatest advantages of bodyweight training is that you can do it anywhere, anytime.</li>\r\n 	<li>There are easier and more advanced exercises to start or evolve with that makes the sport suitable for athletes of all skill and fitness levels.</li>\r\n 	<li>Beginners as well as advanced athletes will find a goal to pursue with the sport. Besides the standard claims of many sports and fitness programms, bodyweight training does not only increase your general fitness and get you in great shape, but provides multiple benefits in addition for you.</li>\r\n 	<li>Proper bodyweight training will promote the growth of lean muscle mass, and increase your strength, mobility, flexibility, agility, and endurance.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nAs you see from the list of benefits of the sport, there is a fine line to <strong><a href=\"http://ykings.com/index.php/competitive-gymnastics/\">competitive gymnastics</a></strong>. In Ykings PBT we embedded the adaptive nature of the sport in a comprehensive workout concept. If you want to be more than just fit, let us hunt down skills and evolve you to a bodyweight master. Welcome to our world.\r\n\r\n</div>','Bodyweight Training & Calisthenics','','inherit','closed','closed','','1415-revision-v1','','','2016-08-29 17:03:45','2016-08-29 17:03:45','',1415,'http://ykings.com/1415-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1732,1,'2016-08-29 17:10:21','2016-08-29 17:10:21','Ykings PBT was developed to bring a new purpose in your sport life. Designed not just to get you in shape but also to increase your mobility, strength, flexibility and body awareness while you hunt down insane bodyweight skills is why we developed this comprehensive workout concept.\r\n\r\nEquipped with an individualized and adaptive coach, users can simply choose their goals and wanted bodyweight skills and start to go after multiple goals at once. Ykings PBT is available on iOs and Android.\r\n\r\nIn the free version, athletes can start a free body workout program that covers all basics. Additionally athletes can get a glimpse of skill train