yweight master. Welcome to our world.\r\n\r\n</div>','Bodyweight Training & Calisthenics','','inherit','closed','closed','','1415-revision-v1','','','2016-08-30 10:03:31','2016-08-30 10:03:31','',1415,'http://ykings.com/1415-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1739,1,'2016-08-30 10:04:52','2016-08-30 10:04:52','PBT is based on the disciplines <strong><a href=\"http://ykings.com/what-is-calisthenics/\">bodyweight training</a></strong> and <a href=\"http://ykings.com/index.php/competitive-gymnastics/\"><strong>gymnastics</strong></a>. Both sports are reknown for the most demanding body control and challenging bodyweight skills.<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nMastering a  bodyweight skill requires to go at it step by step. The adaptive nature of the sport and your progress towards a skill is embedded in essential exercises called progressions. This is why at Ykings we refer our workout concept to progressive bodyweight training (PBT).\r\n\r\nProgressive bodyweight training (PBT) secures gradual development towards advanced bodyweight exercises and skills such as the muscleup, human flag, front lever to name a few.\r\n\r\nThe purpose of the Ykings workout concept is to guide you efficiently and healthy towards mastering your most desirable bodyweight skills. Consider to workout not only for your fitness, but strength, body control and skills and many more beneficial body characteristics at the same time.\r\n\r\n<em>#StriveForProgress</em>','Progressive Bodyweight Training (PBT)','','inherit','closed','closed','','616-revision-v1','','','2016-08-30 10:04:52','2016-08-30 10:04:52','',616,'http://ykings.com/616-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1740,1,'2016-08-30 10:06:09','2016-08-30 10:06:09','<strong>Ykings PBT</strong> was developed to bring a new purpose in your sport life. Designed to not just get you in shape but also to increase your mobility, strength, flexibility and body awareness while you hunt down insane bodyweight skills is why we developed this comprehensive wor